1
00:00:04,100 --> 00:00:05,550
Carica, Haemus!

2
00:00:09,825 --> 00:00:10,775
Non farti prendere dal panico, Lumi!

3
00:00:11,100 --> 00:00:12,350
Ricordi il tuo addestramento?

4
00:00:12,850 --> 00:00:13,950
Sono qui.

5
00:00:14,525 --> 00:00:15,300
Pronti...

6
00:00:16,025 --> 00:00:16,525
Ora!

7
00:00:16,850 --> 00:00:17,375
Salta!

8
00:00:18,950 --> 00:00:19,575
Attacca!

9
00:00:21,325 --> 00:00:22,400
Fermala!

10
00:00:44,850 --> 00:00:45,575
Attenzione!

11
00:00:49,850 --> 00:00:51,350
Questo è il volere del destino...

12
00:00:52,900 --> 00:00:54,650
È finita prima ancora di cominciare.

13
00:01:00,850 --> 00:01:01,425
Lumi!

14
00:01:01,950 --> 00:01:02,750
Lumi...

15
00:01:06,675 --> 00:01:07,075
Ah!

16
00:01:12,450 --> 00:01:12,900
Oh?!

17
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:14,800
Vuoi venire con me?

18
00:01:15,875 --> 00:01:16,650
Andiamo, allora!

19
00:01:17,425 --> 00:01:19,250
Il vasto mondo ci aspetta!

20
00:01:31,150 --> 00:01:33,775
Ya-ho!!!

21
00:01:39,300 --> 00:01:40,025
Ma che...?

22
00:01:57,550 --> 00:01:58,550
Non temere, Haemus.

23
00:01:59,300 --> 00:02:00,500
La vittoria sarà nostra!

24
00:02:19,700 --> 00:02:20,675
La profezia...

